<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="How_To_Apply"></a> How To Apply </span></h2>
<p />
<strong>Important Dates</strong>
<p />
Application Deadline: Jan 25. --> To apply please complete the <a href="http://www.ci.uchicago.edu/events/registrations/tugs08/application.php" target="_top">online application form</a>
The application requires your CV and Letter of Intent in .pdf format. If you need, a simple conversion tool for your .doc files can be found at <a href="https://www.pdfonline.com/convert_pdf.asp" target="_top">https://www.pdfonline.com/convert_pdf.asp</a>
Another note: if your browser gives you the message "Not recommended" while cliking the link above, please do go ahead and access the site. It is safe, but for a more detailed explanation click <a href="/bin/view/Education/ServerCert" class="twikiLink">here</a>.
<p />
Notification of Acceptance will be sent by Jan 26.
<p />
Registration Deadline: Jan 26.
<p />
